<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-01-12T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-01-12T15:00:00-05:00" n="590" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d590">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/3178: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Crane</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-01-12T15:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">January
                                            12, 1921—3 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                            <p>18. Your 9, January 6, 7 p.m.<note n="43" xml:id="d590fn43">Not
                                    printed.</note> The Agreement is the essential thing to be
                                communicated whether by the Groups or by the Legations, even though
                                the question of communicating resolutions be held over until
                                unanimity can be reached among those interested.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>